Package es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.octree

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    Class representing the geometric information of cell in Java (position and size).
    JOctree
    This class wraps an octree object in the Octomap library to be used in java; native wrapped functions include the following: Translation between world coordinates and map keys.
    JOctreeKey
    Represents a key of the JOctree, which is the identifier used to store the nodes in the data structure.
    JOctreeNode
    Represents a node of the JOctree, which is identified with a unique JOctreeKey.
